tom marusak – comfortex skip to content menu november   ashley jackman tom marusak president            thomas j marusak tom is the founder and president of comfortex corporation an international manufacturer of decorative window covering products employing over  people and headquartered in maplewood new york prior to starting comfortex he worked as product development manager for mechanical technology inc in latham new york mr marusak was educated in the engineering and marketing fields he earned degrees from pennsylvania state university an ms from stanford university and pursued an mba at rensselaer polytechnic institute mr marusak is very active in community and business organizations in new york’s capital region in addition to his involvement with several window covering organizations mr marusak currently serves as a member of the board of directors of the capital district physicians health plan cdphp and of mechanical technology inc mti mr marusak formerly served as – president of the chief executive network cen for manufacturing in the capital region – chairman of the center for economic growth ceg – member of the board of directors of the new york state energy research and development authority – advisory board member of dynabil industries inc and keybank of new york – executive board member of albanycolonie chamber of commerce – a congressional appointee to the white house council for small business     thomas j marusak board dir mechanical technology inc a publisher of business information since         search business search executive   advanced search   sign in    hints profile of thomas marusak   thomas marusak   board dir  mechanical technology inc   thomas marusak email  please login   company name  mechanical technology inc   company website  wwwmechtechcom   company address   new karner rd albany nyunited states   thomas marusak profile  board dir  mechanical technology inc   thomas marusak biography  mr marusak was appointed to mti�s board of direc